long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: With this extension you can take time-stamped notes while watching YouTube videos. Press Alt+P, the video will stop playing, a prompt will show up, write your note and press Alt+Enter. Your timestamped notes will appear at the bottom of the video. Hit the Shift key with the previous commands to take a snapshot! You can find more shortcuts and customize them.
